       S8000-ERRMSG-RTN.

      *   거래시각
           MOVE  FUNCTION  CURRENT-DATE(9:6)
             TO  WK-TRAN-HMS

      *   거래시각　２０시?２２시이면　２２시　이후　거래메세지
           IF (WK-TRAN-HMS > CO-CHA-200000 AND
               WK-TRAN-HMS < CO-CHA-220000)
               STRING CO-MSG1
                      CO-MSG2
               DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  WK-MSG
           ELSE
      *   거래시각　１３시이전이면　１３시　이후　거래메세지
               IF WK-TRAN-HMS < CO-CHA-130000
                  STRING CO-MSG1
                         CO-MSG3
                  DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  WK-MSG
               ELSE
      *   거래시각　그외이면　잠시후　거래메세지
                  STRING CO-MSG1
                         CO-MSG4
                  DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO  WK-MSG
               END-IF
           END-IF

      *   사용자　메세지　에러　발생
           #CSTMSG WK-MSG       CO-SUBMSG
